    (F : @Functor Unit Unit (Category.Monoid α) (Category.Monoid β)) :
    ∃ f: α →* β, ∀ x: α, @CategoryInContext.Functor.homF Unit Unit (Category.Monoid α) (Category.Monoid β) F () () x = f x := by
  have h₁ : ∃ (f : α → β), (∀ (x y : α), f (x * y) = f x * f y) ∧ f 1 = 1 := by sorry
  sorry
```

